[heading Introduction to GraphQL]

The Kenshi Deep Indexing GraphQL service serves as your gateway to efficiently
query blockchain data stored within Kenshi's blockchain data clusters. Adhering
to the standard GraphQL specification, this user-friendly endpoint is accessible
via HTTP protocol using POST requests, streamlining data retrieval and
management in the blockchain ecosystem.

To use the GraphQL service, you will need an API key. To create an API key, visit
the Kenshi [link https://timeleap.swiss/dashboard dashboard]. Continue reading to get help
with the dashboard or see examples of the Sync service.
